commit message: Ability to create 'checkins'. This feature is disabled, because presently Pump.io thinks they are major activities

Bugfix for video objects. We display a 'preview' now and link out to an external video player when a stream is listed. This will enable viewing videos posted with the experimental post video feature in Dianara.
Insert activities into the DB as activities, not objects. This makes your own comments show up quicker
